":"師兄識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要唔係個課程大綱 同教法   而係考法 引導到學生點諗<br />\n<br />\n要你諗下AIDS既好處   就同要你諗  有毒氣體如何無害   農民如何從油價上漲中得溢 一樣  思考過程係有趣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719784489e6ecb19e1da5bdf9f00ebc78d9d7e70","tid":990452,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pQDiXU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pQDiXU.png&h=32a9d7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SGCzwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SGCzwg.png&h=f6ae3a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be6733493f2afb4c668e302b1ac39ccc6db647f","tid":990452,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"愛滋病肆虐<br />\n中國或成最大贏家"}]}